{"tid":350314,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你考慮緊入唔入樹大既入一入黎","createTime":"2017-08-07T06:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T13:57:35.000Z","uid":70817,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49b4629f340390c6bbdaa5865eb490b73d5a6ada","tid":350314,"uid":70817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:53:53.000Z","msg":"樹大本身有咩問題我就唔多講先,<br />\n詳情請見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/293431/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/293431/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完呢篇都仲改變唔到你入樹大既話,<br />\n麻煩你諗清楚以下問題:<br />\n<br />\n1. 樹大基本上全部都係枯枝, 入得黎都冇心向學、求鳩其要個degree, <br />\n你係咪淨係想求個垃圾degree就算?<br />\n<br />\n2. 點解唔考慮asso 走後門入三大, dse唔掂唔代表asso一定死。只要肯勤力d 英文唔係差到貼地既asso大把機會上番8大。你係咪甘心放棄由asso入番8大既機會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\np.s. 唔好講咩trans u, asso走到既機會大過你所謂既trans u幾百倍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 入樹大同讀中學冇乜分別, 如果你想要咩ulife既話, 麻煩你唔洗諗。 咁你諗清楚你追求既係乜未? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 讀asso唔掂仲可以番轉頭讀垃圾樹大, cgpa過2.5就收你(智商正常就有2.5, 唔過2.5其實係唔適合讀書)。 asso咁大條後路你係咪應該考慮左asso先呢？<br />\n<br />\n5. 如果你貪3萬資助既話, 你諗下係咪每年3萬蚊就買得起你前途？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總"},{"pid":"544116bf7051d50610a90022a495edb7a17d0e7c","tid":350314,"uid":70817,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:56:09.000Z","msg":"總之樹大又好, 乜柒自資院校都好, 都係垃圾讀既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64970a37fcdde3c0935e8bdf287be93f40eac668","tid":350314,"uid":70817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c287f2e220d0ba969a50cc9d7e608a3125189f","tid":350314,"uid":36857,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:13:58.000Z","msg":"認真，當年dse放榜就入開樹痕嗰班真係做咗傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年班dse 1x分中同醒嘅去晒讀asso，2年後咪又係一條好漢，hkcc嗰班好似全部入到ugc，其他asso就一半半啦<br />\n不過前提係你要有心再捱多2年，想hea嘅就直入開樹痕算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3ee23b48881606e2f0906970b6edd2c715cf5b","tid":350314,"uid":70817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:16:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真，當年dse放榜就入開樹痕嗰班真係做咗傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年班dse 1x分中同醒嘅去晒讀asso，2年後咪又係一條好漢，hkcc嗰班好似全部入到ugc，其他asso就一半半啦<br />\n不過前提係你要有心再捱多2年，想hea嘅就直入開樹痕算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nasso一定冇想像中咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a226969ffa00ac1e84a61dc075ff88e9190dc213","tid":350314,"uid":12536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T07:43:48.000Z","msg":"asso要識揀科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nasso揀soc sci/文科果啲都死得幾慘下<br />\n工科商科基本上都上到ugc<br />\n當然要係本身18-20 range嘅人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63c9b9392edd581ad8cc7b19d4cb485e95813c8","tid":350314,"uid":70817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1ad85c4f2b3b87799004f953096e5fe270a3e1","tid":350314,"uid":70817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T13:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d468c184939bfd48874fc2e5b4c739596663699a","tid":350314,"uid":38554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08